	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b5b8a0971c2940faccafb60e2bb060ab2.png"></span><span>Flamewyrm's Nature III</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to burning by 100%.<br>When Mym is hit by an attack that would have<br>inflicted her with burn, her strength is increased<br>by 15% for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff<br>will not activate again for 15 seconds.<br><br>Also, when shapeshifting for the first time, Mym<br>will transform into Brunhilda regardless of what<br>dragon she is equipped with, her strength will<br>increase by 15% for the remainder of the quest,<br>and the skill Flames of Passion will be powered<br>up for the remainder of the quest. The second time<br>onwards, she will transform into High Brunhilda<br>instead, and her attack rate while shapeshifted<br>will increase by 15%.<br><br>In addition, using a skill will grant Mym a<br>strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of three. After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 30 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/28c0b4387ec47573e89a7e34a452fa012.png"></span><span>Flamewyrm's Defiance III</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun and sleep by 100%.<br>When Mym is hit by an attack that would have<br>stunned or put her to sleep, the skill gauge for<br>the Dragon Claw skill fills by 50%, and her<br>strength is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>these effects cannot be activated again by the<br>same affliction for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f95daa91eaca6e0d41a23320398a9e792.png"></span><span>Dragon Time +25%</span></dt><dd><div>Extends shapeshift time by 25%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes 